id: pm-7811
title: Install and validate pm-changelog package
description: "Install pm-changelog in this repository, verify SDK/package compatibility, generate the repository changelog, wire automation into CI/CD, and record or fix any issues found."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[5]: changelog,ci,packages,release,sdk
created_at: "2026-05-23T20:25:40.368Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T23:29:42.605Z"
author: codex-pm-changelog
parent: pm-59gj
resolution: "Installed latest npm pm-changelog 2026.5.24-1, fixed pm-cli npm package runtime dependency installation for extension SDK imports, wired CI/release changelog checks to install and use the package, generated CHANGELOG.pm.md through pm changelog generate, filed upstream pm-changelog#4 for package sourcemap warnings, and verified linked package, changelog, release, and dogfood gates."
expected_result: pm-cli installs and loads the latest npm pm-changelog package without manual changelog scripts; pm-changelog can generate the repository changelog; CI/CD release gates verify the package-generated changelog and npm/npx/bun release path.
actual_result: "Latest npm pm-changelog installs and loads with changelog generate active; CHANGELOG.pm.md is generated and checked through the package command; CI/release scripts refresh the package before generation; package doctor, linked tests, static release slice, run-gates slice, and package-first dogfood passed."
comments[18]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T20:25:40.368Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Duplicate check: searched for 'pm-changelog changelog package release CI'. Existing package-first lineage pm-59gj is canonical; no dedicated open pm-changelog integration item existed, so this child task tracks the requested work."
  "2026-05-23T20:25:59.418Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Baseline before install: pm package explore/manage/doctor in project scope reported zero project packages and ok=true; npm latest for pm-changelog is 2026.5.23-1 with @unbrained/pm-cli peer >=2026.5.14."
  "2026-05-23T20:26:49.874Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Issue found: installed pm-changelog exposes help/contracts, but runtime generation failed: pm changelog generate --stdout --title 'pm CLI Changelog' --release-version Unreleased --status closed --group-by version exits with extension_command_handler_failed. Investigating whether this is package handler logic or SDK surface."
  "2026-05-23T20:39:19.289Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Upstream fix: pm-changelog issue #1 filed, fixed in unbraind/pm-changelog commit 2a3c4bb, and direct npm run release:check passed there. npm publish of 2026.5.23-2 is blocked from this shell by npm 2FA policy, so this repo will install the fixed package from GitHub ref 2a3c4bb until an authorized npm publisher publishes the version."
  "2026-05-23T20:44:08.323Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Implementation update: removed the local wrapper approach. pm-cli now calls the installed pm-changelog package command directly via node dist/cli.js changelog generate. Generated CHANGELOG.pm.md is package-owned and checked by CI/release through pnpm changelog:pm:check."
  "2026-05-23T20:47:55.235Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Upstream package final status: pm-changelog fix is now commit a99e8ff with green GitHub CI run 26343165489. This includes large JSON buffer handling, manifest version alignment, and extension --check nonzero failure when generated changelog is stale. pm-cli reinstalled that GitHub package revision."
  "2026-05-23T20:59:58.224Z",codex-pm-changelog-integrator,"Evidence: CI static gate failed on the first push because GitHub-source pm-changelog install included upstream tracker data with a local absolute path. Opened unbraind/pm-changelog#2, fixed upstream with pm history-redact at 0acca83160d2f9689b9e5f027cc49fb481686006, reinstalled via pm install --gh, and local static gate sequence now passes including pnpm changelog:pm:check and pnpm security:scan."
  "2026-05-23T21:05:02.310Z",codex-pm-changelog-integrator,"Evidence: CI static gate for 68f80d49 failed because the installed GitHub package's dist/ payload was ignored by pm-changelog's nested .gitignore and therefore absent from the checkout; node dist/cli.js could not load the extension entry and reported Unknown command changelog. Fixing by force-adding the installed package dist files produced by pm install --gh."
  "2026-05-23T21:21:12.041Z",codex-pm-changelog-integrator,"Evidence: upstream pm-changelog issues #1 and #3 are fixed and closed. Installed pm-changelog 2026.5.23-5 from GitHub main at f5ebc23c7e3dbc9d41ac687b14826fe5632e9d1a via pm install; upstream CI run 26343824903 passed. Package doctor is clean with runtime command changelog generate active; pnpm changelog:pm:check reports unchanged CHANGELOG.pm.md with 788 items. Local static gate passed: pnpm version:check && pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm security:scan && pnpm quality:static && npm pack --dry-run. Npm publish of 2026.5.23-5 is blocked by npm E403 requiring 2FA or a bypass-2FA token, so this repo is pinned to the verified GitHub source until authorized publish."
  "2026-05-23T21:29:28.759Z",codex-pm-changelog-integrator,"Evidence update: after closing pm-bu50, CHANGELOG.pm.md was stale by one closed item. Regenerated it with the installed pm-changelog package via pnpm changelog:pm; pnpm changelog:pm:check now reports item_count=789 and local static gate passes again."
  "2026-05-23T22:35:09.510Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Investigation note: GitHub issue check found unbraind/pm-cli#53 open for npm package dependency resolution; pm-changelog repo currently has no open issues; npm latest pm-changelog is 2026.5.24-1."
  "2026-05-23T23:01:05.559Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Evidence: reproduced unbraind/pm-cli#53 in a clean temp project with pm-changelog@2026.5.24-1, then fixed npm-backed package runtime dependency installation. Clean temp project now installs npm:pm-changelog and runs pm changelog generate successfully."
  "2026-05-23T23:10:59.569Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Investigation note: linked static slice must run with tracker pm context because pm-changelog compares generated output against real tracker-derived CHANGELOG.pm.md; schema-only sandbox correctly lacks the 773 closed-item changelog input."
  "2026-05-23T23:17:08.307Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Issue found and fixed: release gate npx smoke passed functionally but failed cleanup with ENOTEMPTY removing /tmp/pm-pack-smoke-*; hardened scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs cleanup with fs.rmSync retries."
  "2026-05-23T23:21:28.853Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Verification evidence: linked tests passed for package doctor, focused integration, build, tracker-context pnpm changelog:pm:check, and tracker-context CI static release slice. Release gate slice passed with --skip-dogfood --skip-telemetry-sentry: build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, coverage 1569 tests, version, secret scan, npx smoke, npm pack, compatibility."
  "2026-05-23T23:22:09.219Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Verification evidence: pnpm dogfood:package-first passed in /tmp/pm-dogfood-5xm1rL with 84 commands; semantic dogfood skipped because PM_DOGFOOD_SEMANTIC was not set."
  "2026-05-23T23:26:31.113Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Upstream package issue filed: unbraind/pm-changelog#4 tracks published sourcemaps that point to missing source files. This is package-side packaging hygiene; pm-cli continues using the published package as-is."
  "2026-05-23T23:27:11.080Z",codex-changelog-integration,"Verification evidence: release-readiness-runtime focused test passed after reverting accidental CHANGELOG.md rewrite: 32 tests passed."
